# Personal brand-logo uploads stay LOCAL — do not ship your own marks.
# (The blanket *.png rule above already ignores them.) The logo resolver
# auto-fetches marks by company name/domain, so a fresh clone needs no uploads.
# Track only the neutral sample placeholders so the example renders.
!integrations/hermes-job-hunt/resume-template/uploads/logo-sample.png
!integrations/hermes-job-hunt/resume-template/uploads/logo-sample-co.png
